WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:04.900 --> 00:00:07.200
Sarge...look at the moon...

00:00:09.160 --> 00:00:12.900
[chuckles] it's
funny....you never noticed how

00:00:12.900 --> 00:00:14.800
beautiful the moons are here...

00:00:16.400 --> 00:00:18.320
[chuckles] you think anybody noticed?

00:00:18.320 --> 00:00:18.820
[static]

00:00:18.820 --> 00:00:21.740
[grunt growls] [plasma fire] [Elite roars]

00:00:21.940 --> 00:00:22.440
[static]

00:00:22.700 --> 00:00:26.380
stay quiet. the biofoam's working but you're
still bleeding.

00:00:27.620 --> 00:00:33.800
there's something I've always wanted to know...your call sign, ghost. what
does it mean?

00:00:33.840 --> 00:00:37.220
[static] weapons free! [gunfire] [plasma fire]

00:00:37.280 --> 00:00:41.520
stop talking. you've gotta hold
tight until the med-evac gets here.

00:00:41.880 --> 00:00:47.020
you finally have an excuse to show that you care...and...

00:00:47.300 --> 00:00:50.799
[static] [plasma fire] [marines dying] [static]

00:00:53.740 --> 00:01:03.360
let me ask you something...just one last thing...it
won't hurt. I promise. what was I to you?

00:01:03.760 --> 00:01:10.660
what do you mean? you're a soldier. a soldier
with a promising future ahead of you...

00:01:10.660 --> 00:01:12.620
you're...a soldier.

00:01:12.620 --> 00:01:14.640
and you're a ghost, aren't you?

00:01:15.900 --> 00:01:16.400
what?

00:01:16.860 --> 00:01:18.980
feelings pass right through you, don't they?

00:01:19.800 --> 00:01:23.140
so cold and unforgiving in every choice
you made in battle.

00:01:24.020 --> 00:01:27.720
Pure soldier. I think that's what let us trust you--

00:01:27.720 --> 00:01:29.360
don't talk. save your strength.

00:01:29.360 --> 00:01:30.240
I don't need it

00:01:30.240 --> 00:01:30.740
[gasp]

00:01:31.340 --> 00:01:36.060
I need you to be strong. strong enough to
do what you've never done in your life.

00:01:37.520 --> 00:01:40.740
can you be strong enough to allow yourself to
be...

00:01:41.820 --> 00:01:43.740
Can you just be human?

